title: AOC Debuts on Twitch - Kinda Funny Games Daily 10.21.20
description:
MinnMax's Ben Hanson joins Greg to talk about Alexandria Ocasio-Cortez's Twitch debut, Fortnite getting Ghostbusters, and Twitch purging thousands of videos! Support MinnMax at http://www.patreon.com/minnmax!
